"Ringkaskan ukuran efek dan estimasi heterogenitas yang digunakan untuk "
"diagram corong di bawah hipotesis alternatif dalam tabel."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Fixed value for the mean effect size under the alternative hypothesis."
msgstr "Nilai tetap untuk ukuran efek rerata di bawah hipotesis alternatif."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid ""
"Fixed value for 𝜏, representing the heterogeneity under the alternative "
"hypothesis."
msgstr ""
"Nilai tetap untuk 𝜏, merepresentasikan heterogenitas di bawah hipotesis "
"alternatif."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid ""
"Fill the funnel plot's prediction intervals under the alternative hypothesis "
"with different colors."
msgstr ""
"Isi interval prediksi diagram corong di bawah hipotesis alternatif dengan "
"berbagai warna."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid ""
"Set the type of line of the funnel plot's prediction intervals under the "
"alternative hypothesis."
msgstr ""
"Atur jenis garis dari interval prediksi diagram corong di bawah hipotesis "
"alternatif."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Power enhancement"
msgstr "Peningkatan keberdayaan"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid ""
"Visualize power levels to detect the effect size under the alternative "
"hypothesis with alpha = 0.05."
msgstr ""
"Visualisasikan tingkat keberdayaan untuk mendeteksi ukuran efek di bawah "
"hipotesis alternatif dengan alfa = 0.05."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Breaks"
msgstr "Jeda"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid ""
"Specify the breakpoints for power enhancement. All levels must be within the "
"0.05 - 1 range."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan titik jeda untuk peningkatan keberdayaan. Semua tingkat harus dalam "
"rentang 0.05 - 1."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Estimates Mapping"
msgstr "Pemetaan Estimasi"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid ""
"Set mapping for labels, colors, and shapes of the effect size estimates."
msgstr ""
"Atur pemetaan untuk label, warna, dan bentuk dari estimasi ukuran efek."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Label"
msgstr "Label"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Show all or only a subset of the effect size estimate labels."
msgstr ""
"Tampilkan semua atau hanya subrangkaian dari label estimasi ukuran efek."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "All"
msgstr "Semua"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Outside H₀"
msgstr "Di luar H₀"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Outside H₁"
msgstr "Di luar H₁"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Color"
msgstr "Warna"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid ""
"Map colors of the effect size estimates in the funnel plot based on the "
"selected variable."
msgstr ""
"Petakan warna dari estimasi ukuran efek dalam diagram corong berdasarkan "
"variabel terpilih."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Shape"
msgstr "Bentuk"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid ""
"Map shapes of the effect size estimates in the funnel plot based on the "
"selected variable."
msgstr ""
"Petakan bentuk dari estimasi ukuran efek dalam diagram corong berdasarkan "
"variabel terpilih."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Legend position"
msgstr "Posisi legenda"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid ""
"Set the legend position of the funnel plot. Available when color or shape "
"mapping is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Atur posisi legenda dari diagram corong. Tersedia ketika pemetaan warna atau "
"bentuk diaktifkan."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Bottom"
msgstr "Bawah"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Right"
msgstr "Kanan"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Top"
msgstr "Atas"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Left"
msgstr "Kiri"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Label offset"
msgstr "Imbangan label"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Adjust the offset of labels in the funnel plot."
msgstr "Sesuaikan imbangan label dalam diagram corong."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Funnel prediction interval"
msgstr "Interval prediksi corong"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Specify the confidence levels for the funnel plot prediction intervals."
msgstr "Tentukan tingkat kepercayaan untuk interval prediksi diagram corong."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Invert colors"
msgstr "Balikkan warna"

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Invert the colors used in the funnel plot."
msgstr "Balikkan warna yang digunakan dalam diagram corong."

msgctxt "FunnelPlot|"
msgid "Meta-regression"
msgstr "Meta-regresi"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Lanjutan"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Advanced options for the meta-analysis, including optimization settings, "
"clustering, and permutation tests."
msgstr ""
"Opsi lanjutan untuk meta-analisis, mencakup pengaturan optimisasi, "
"keklasteran, dan uji permutasi."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Show metafor R code"
msgstr "Tampilkan kode R metafot"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Display the underlying R code used by the metafor package to fit the model."
msgstr ""
"Tampilkan kode R yang mendasari digunakan oleh paket metafor untuk "
"menyesuaikan model."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Weighted estimation"
msgstr "Estimasi terberat"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Perform weighted estimation using inverse-variance weights. Uncheck for "
"unweighted estimation."
msgstr ""
"Lakukan estimasi terberat menggunakan berat varians-terbalik. Hapus centang "
"untuk estimasi tidak berberat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Clustering"
msgstr "Keklasteran"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Use clubSandwich"
msgstr "Gunakan clubSandwich"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Use the clubSandwich package for robust variance estimation in clustered "
"data. Enabled when a clustering variable is specified."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan paket clubSandwich untuk estimasi varians kekuatan dalam data "
"terklaster. Diaktifkan ketika variabel keklasteran ditentukan."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Small sample correction"
msgstr "Koreksi sampel kecil"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Apply a small-sample correction to the clustered standard errors."
msgstr "Terapkan koreksi sampel-kecil ke galat standar terklaster."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Random Effects / Modele Structure"
msgstr "Efek Acak / Struktur Modele"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Use sparse matricies"
msgstr "Gunakan matriks jarang"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Use sparse matrix representations to speed up computations in models with "
"large datasets or complex random effects structures. Available in multilevel/"
"multivariate meta-analysis."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan representasi matriks jarang untuk mempercepat perhitungan dalam "
"model dengan rangkaian data besar atau struktur efek acak kompleks. Tersedia "
"dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/multivariat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Compute covariance matrix"
msgstr "Hitung matriks kovarians"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Compute the covariance matrix of the parameter estimates. Available in "
"multilevel/multivariate meta-analysis."
msgstr ""
"Hitung matriks kovarians dari estimasi parameter. Tersedia dalam meta-"
"analisis multitingkat/mutlivariat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Fix Parameters"
msgstr "Perbaiki Parameter"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "𝜏²"
msgstr "𝜏²"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Fix the value of 𝜏² in the model instead of estimating it. Unavailable in "
"multilevel/multivariate meta-analysis or with meta-regression model for "
"heterogeneity. A more complex heterogeneity terms in the multilevel/"
"multivariate meta-analysis can be fixed via the 'Extend metafor call' option."
msgstr ""
"Perbaiki nilai dari 𝜏² dalam model alih-alih mengestimasinya. Tidak tersedia "
"dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/multivariat atau degan model meta-regresi "
"untuk heterogenitas. Istilah heterogentias yang lebih kompleks dalam meta-"
"analisis multitingkat/multivariat dapat diperbaiki melalui opsi 'Luaskan "
"panggilan metafor'."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Weights"
msgstr "Berat"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Use custom weights for the effect sizes instead of inverse-variance weights."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan berat kustom untuk ukuran efek alih-alih berat varians terbalik."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Add Omibus Moderator Test"
msgstr "Tambahkan Uji Moderator Omibus"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Effect size coefficients"
msgstr "Koefisien ukuran efek"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Include an omnibus test for the specified effect size regression "
"coefficients. Available when effect size model terms are included. The "
"coefficients should be selected via their comma-separated indicies which "
"correspond to the order presented in the 'Effect Size Meta-Regression "
"Coefficients' Table."
msgstr ""
"Sertakan uji omnibus untuk koefisien regresi ukuran efek yang ditentukan. "
"Tersedia ketika istilah model ukuran efek disertakan. Koefisien harus "
"dipilih melalui indeks yang dipisahkan koma yang sesuai dengan urutan yang "
"dipresentasikan dalam Tabel 'Koefisien Meta-Regresi Ukuran Efek'."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Specify the indices of the effect size meta-regression coefficients to "
"include in the omnibus test, e.g. '(1, 2)' for the first and the second "
"coefficient."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan indeks dari koefisien meta-regresi ukuran efek yang disertakan "
"dalam uji omnibus, mis. '(1, 2)' untuk koefisien pertama dan kedua."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Heterogeneity coefficients"
msgstr "Koefisien heterogenitas"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Include an omnibus test for the specified heterogeneity regression "
"coefficients. Available when heterogeneity model terms are included. The "
"coefficients should be selected via their comma-separated indicies which "
"correspond to the order presented in the 'Heterogeneity Meta-Regression "
"Coefficients' Table."
msgstr ""
"Sertakan uji omnibus untuk koefisien regresi heterogenitas yang ditentukan. "
"Tersedia ketika istilah model heterogenitas disertakan. Koefisien harus "
"dipilih melalui indeks yang dipisahkan koma yang sesuai dengan urutan yang "
"dipresentasikan dalam Tabel 'Koefisien Meta-Regresi Heterogenitas'."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Specify the indices of the heterogeneity meta-regression coefficients to "
"include in the omnibus test, e.g. '(1, 2)' for the first and the second "
"coefficient."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan indeks dari koefisien meta-regresi heterogenitas yang disertakan "
"dalam uji omnibus, mis. '(1, 2)' untuk koefisien pertama dan kedua."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Optimizer"
msgstr "Pengoptimisasi"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Optimizer settings for estimating the meta-analytic models. A more complex/"
"unavailbe settings can be specified via the 'Extend metafor call' option."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan pengoptimisasi untuk mengestimasi model meta-analisis. Pengaturan "
"yang lebih kompleks/tidak tersedia dapat ditentukan melalui opsi 'Luaskan "
"panggilan metafor'."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Method"
msgstr "Metode"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Select the optimization method to use for fitting the model. Available in "
"multilevel/multivariate meta-analysis or when heterogeneity model terms are "
"included."
msgstr ""
"Pilih metode optimisasi yang digunakan untuk menyesuaikan model. Tersedia "
"dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/multivariat atau ketika istilah model "
"heterogenitas disertakan."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Initial 𝜏²"
msgstr "Awal 𝜏²"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Specify the initial value of 𝜏² for the optimization algorithm. Available "
"only for specific optimization methods and unavailable in multilevel/"
"multivariate meta-analysis or when heterogeneity model terms are included."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan nilai awal dari 𝜏² untuk algoritma optimisasi. Tersedia hanya untuk "
"metode optimisasi spesifik dan tidak tersedia dalam meta-analisis "
"multitingkat/multivariat atau ketika istilah model heterogenitas disertakan."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Minimum 𝜏²"
msgstr "Minimum 𝜏²"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Specify the minimum allowable value of 𝜏² during optimization. Available "
"only for specific optimization methods and unavailable in multilevel/"
"multivariate meta-analysis or when heterogeneity model terms are included."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan nilai minimum yang dapat diizinkan dari 𝜏² selama optimisasi. "
"Tersedia hanya untuk metode optimisasi spesifik dan tidak tersedia dalam "
"meta-analisis multitingkat/multivariat atau ketika istilah model "
"heterogenitas disertakan."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Maximum 𝜏²"
msgstr "Maksimum 𝜏²"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Maximum evaluations"
msgstr "Evaluasi maksimum"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Set the maximum number of function evaluations for the optimizer. Available "
"when using specific optimization methods in multilevel/multivariate meta-"
"analysis."
msgstr ""
"Atur jumlah maksimum evaluasi fungsi untuk pengoptimisasi. Tersedia ketika "
"menggunakan metode optimisasi spesifik dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/"
"multivariat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Maximum iterations"
msgstr "Iterasi maksimum"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Set the maximum number of iterations for the optimizer. Available when using "
"certain estimation or optimization methods."
msgstr ""
"Atur jumlah maksimum iterasi untuk pengoptimisasi. Tersedia ketika "
"menggunakan estimasi tertentu atau metode optimisasi."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Convergence tolerance"
msgstr "Toleransi konvergensi"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Set the convergence tolerance for the optimizer. Available when using "
"certain methods without heterogeneity model terms or specific optimizers in "
"multilevel/multivariate meta-analysis."
msgstr ""
"Atur toleransi konvergensi untuk pengoptimisasi. Tersedia ketika menggunakan "
"metode tertentu tanpa istilah model heterogenitas atau pengoptimisasi "
"spesifik dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/multivariat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Convergence relative tolerance"
msgstr "Toleransi relatif konvergensi"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Set the relative convergence tolerance for the optimizer. Available when "
"heterogeneity model terms are included or using specific optimizers in "
"multilevel/multivariate meta-analysis."
msgstr ""
"Atur toleransi konvergensi relatif untuk pengoptimisasi. Tersedia ketika "
"istilah model heterogenitas disertakan atau menggunakan pengoptimisasi "
"spesifik dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/multivariat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Step adjustment"
msgstr "Penyesuaian langkah"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Set the step adjustment factor for the optimizer. Available when using "
"certain methods without heterogeneity model terms and unavailable in "
"multilevel/multivariate meta-analysis."
msgstr ""
"Atur faktor penyesuaian langkah untuk pengoptimisasi. Tersedia ketika "
"menggunakan metode tertentu tanpa istilah model heterogenitas dan tidak "
"tersedia dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/multivariat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Initial trust region radius"
msgstr "Radius wilayah kepercayaan awal"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Set the initial trust region radius for the optimizer. Available when using "
"specific optimization methods in multilevel/multivariate meta-analysis."
msgstr ""
"Atur radius wilayah kepercayaan awal untuk pengoptimisasi. Tersedia ketika "
"menggunakan metode optimisasi spesifik dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/"
"multivariat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Final trust region radius"
msgstr "Radius wilayah kepercayaan akhir"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Set the final trust region radius for the optimizer. Available when using "
"specific optimization methods in multilevel/multivariate meta-analysis."
msgstr ""
"Atur radius wilayah kepercayaan akhir untuk pengoptimisasi. Tersedia ketika "
"menggunakan metode optimisasi spesifik dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/"
"multivariat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Maximum restarts"
msgstr "Pemulaian ulang maksimum"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Set the maximum number of restarts for the optimizer. Available when using "
"the Nelder-Mead method ('nmk') in multilevel/multivariate meta-analysis."
msgstr ""
"Atur jumlah maksimum pemulaian ulang untuk pengoptimisasi. Tersedia ketika "
"menggunakan metode Nelder-Mead ('nmk') dalam meta-analisis multitingkat/"
"multivariat."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Permutation test"
msgstr "Uji permutasi"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Jenis"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Select the type of permutation test."
msgstr "Pilih jenis uji permutasi."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Approximate"
msgstr "Perkiraan"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Exact"
msgstr "Tepat"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Iteration"
msgstr "Iterasi"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"Specify the number of permutations to use in the approximate permutation "
"test."
msgstr "Tentukan jumlah permutasi yang digunakan dalam uji permutasi perkiraan."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid "Extend metafor call"
msgstr "Luaskan panggilan metafor"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisAdvanced|"
msgid ""
"The additional arguments to the metafor function call must be specified as a "
"named list (the 'list()' call can be ommited). E.g., 'list(tau2 = 1)' (or "
"'tau2 = 1') can be used to fix the between-study heterogeneity to a given "
"value. Multiple arguments must be comma-seprated, e.g. 'list(tau2 = 1, "
"gamma2 = 0.5)' (or 'tau2 = 1, gamma2 = 0.5'). New lines are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Argumen tambahan ke panggilan fungsi metafor harus ditentukan sebagai daftar "
"bernama (panggilan 'list()' dapat dihapus). Mis. 'list(tau2 = 1)' (atau "
"'tau2 = 1') dapat digunakan untuk memperbaiki heterogenitas antara-studi ke "
"nilai yang diberikan. Beberapa argumen harus dipisahkan koma, mis. 'list"
"(tau2 = 1, gamma2 = 0.5)' (atau 'tau2 = 1, gamma2 = 0.5'). Baris baru "
"diabaikan."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid ""
"Options for evaluating the influence of individual studies and assessing "
"model diagnostics, including variance inflation factors, casewise "
"diagnostics, and diagnostic plots."
msgstr ""
"Opsi untuk mengevaluasi influens dari studi individu dan mengevaluasi "
"diagnostik model, mencakup faktor inflasi varians, diagnostik per kasus, dan "
"diagram diagnostik."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Variance inflation factor"
msgstr "Faktor inflasi varians"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid ""
"Include variance inflation factors to assess multicollinearity among "
"predictors. Available when predictors are included in the model."
msgstr ""
"Sertakan faktor inflasi varians untuk mengevaluasi multikolinearitas di "
"antara prediktor. Tersedia ketika prediktor disertakan dalam model."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Aggregate by terms"
msgstr "Agregasikan berdasarkan istilah"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid ""
"Aggregate variance inflation factors by terms instead of individual "
"coefficients."
msgstr ""
"Agregasikan faktor inflasi varians berdasarkan istilah alih-alih koefisien "
"individual."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Show influential only"
msgstr "Hanya tampilkan influensial"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Include predictors"
msgstr "Sertakan prediktor"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Include predictor variables in the casewise diagnostics output."
msgstr "Sertakan variabel prediktor dalam luaran diagnostik per kasus."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Difference in coefficients"
msgstr "Perbedaan dalam koefisien"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid ""
"Include the differences in model coefficients when each study is excluded "
"(DFBETAS)."
msgstr ""
"Sertakan perbedaan dalam koefisien model ketika setiap studi dikecualikan "
"(DFBETAS)."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Export to dataset"
msgstr "Ekspor ke rangkaian data"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Export the casewise diagnostics results to the dataset."
msgstr "Ekspor hasil diagnostik per kasus ke rangkaian data."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Influential indicator only"
msgstr "Hanya indikator influensial"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Export only the indicator of influential cases to the dataset."
msgstr "Ekspor hanya indikator dari kasus influensial ke rangkaian data."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Profile likelihood"
msgstr "Kemungkinan profil"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Include a profile likelihood plot for the heterogeneity parameter (τ²)."
msgstr "Sertakan diagram kemungkinan profil untuk parameter heterogenitas (τ²)."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Baujat"
msgstr "Baujat"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisDiagnostics|"
msgid "Residual funnel"
msgstr "Corong residu"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid "Estimated Marginal Means"
msgstr "Rerata Margin Terestimasi"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid "Effect size"
msgstr "Ukuran efek"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid ""
"Variables selected for computing estimated marginal means in the effect size "
"model."
msgstr ""
"Variabel dipilih untuk menghitung rerata margin terestimasi dalam model "
"ukuran efek."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid "SD factor covariates"
msgstr "Kovariat faktor SD"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid ""
"Standard deviation factor for covariates when computing estimated marginal "
"means; applies to scale variables."
msgstr ""
"Faktor deviasi standar untuk kovariat ketika menghitung rerata margin "
"terestimasi; menerapkan ke variabel skala."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid "Add adjusted estimate"
msgstr "Tambahkan estimasi yang disesuaikan"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid ""
"Include the adjusted effect estimate, which accounts for the moderators in "
"the meta-regression model. This provides the effect size adjusted for the "
"influence of moderators, as opposed to the pooled effect which combines the "
"estimates across all studies."
msgstr ""
"Sertakan estimasi efek yang disesuaikan, yang menghitung untuk moderator "
"dalam model meta-regresi. Ini memberikan ukuran efek yang disesuaikan untuk "
"influens moderator, berbeda dengan efek kumpulan yang mengombinasikan "
"estimasi yang melintasi semua studi."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid "Test against"
msgstr "Uji terhadap"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid "Option to test the estimated marginal means against a specific value."
msgstr "Opsi untuk menguji estimasi rerata margin terhadap nilai tertentu."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid "Heterogeneity"
msgstr "Heterogenitas"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid ""
"Include the adjusted heterogeneity estimate, which accounts for the "
"moderators in the heterogeneity meta-regression model. This provides the "
"heterogeneity estimate adjusted for the influence of moderators, as opposed "
"to the pooled heterogeneity estimate which combines the heterogeneity "
"estimates across all studies."
msgstr ""
"Sertakan estimasi heterogenitas yang disesuaikan, yang menghitung untuk "
"moderator dalam model meta-regresi heterogenitas. Ini memberikan estimasi "
"heterogenitas yang disesuaikan untuk influens moderator, berbeda dengan "
"estimasi heterogenitas terkumpul yang mengombinasikan estimasi heterogenitas "
"melintasi semua studi."

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid "Heterogeneity transformation"
msgstr "Transformasi heterogenitas"

msgctxt "ClassicalMetaAnalysisEstimatedMarginalMeans|"
msgid ""
"Transformation to apply to the heterogeneity estimate: tau (𝜏) or tau-"
"squared (𝜏²)."
msgstr ""
