"tertampil dari komponen (jika komponen tidak dipilih, uji faktor Bayes tidak "
"dikonduksikan). Estimasi tertampil dirata-ratakan melintasi distribusi "
"priori null dan alternatif dari semua komponen yang ditentukan."

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Effect size"
msgstr "Ukuran efek"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Average over the presence vs. absence of the effect. If unspecified, the "
"resulting model assumes that the effect is present."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Heterogeneity"
msgstr "Heterogenitas"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Average over the presence vs. absence of heterogeneity. If unspecified, the "
"resulting model assumes that heterogeneity is present."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Moderation"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Average over the presence vs. absence of moderators. If unspecified, the "
"resulting model assumes that all moderators models are present."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Publication bias"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Average over the presence vs. absence of publication bias. If unspecified, "
"the resulting model assumes that publication bias is present."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Prior Distributions"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Effect size and heterogeneity"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Specify the type of prior distributions for the effect size and "
"heterogeneity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Default"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Use default prior distributions for the effect size and heterogeneity based "
"on Bartoš et al. (2022)."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Medicine"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Use prior distributions based on the Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews "
"developed by Bartoš et al. (2021)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Kustom"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Use custom prior distributions. This option allows you to specify a custom "
"model ensemble for the effect size and heterogeneity prior distributions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Use prior distributions based on the Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews "
"developed by Bartoš et al. (2023)."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Scale"
msgstr "Skala"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Setting value different than 1 re-scales the pre-specified prior "
"distributions. Values smaller than 1 lead to more informative priors, while "
"values larger than 1 lead to less informative priors."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Publication bias adjustment"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Publication bias adjustment method. The default is the RoBMA-PSMA method "
"(combination of 6 weight functions and PET-PEESE)."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "RoBMA-PSMA"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"RoBMA-PSMA method (combination of 6 weight functions and PET-PEESE) as "
"described in Bartoš et al. (2022). This is the recommended method."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "RoBMA-PP"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"RoBMA PET-PEESE method. A simplification of the RoBMA-PSMA method that uses "
"only the PET-PEESE weight function."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "RoBMA-original"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Original RoBMA method (combination of 2 weight functions) as described in "
"Maier et al. (2023)."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Custom model ensemble. This option allows you to specify a custom model "
"ensemble for the publication bias adjustment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "None"
msgstr "Tidak Ada"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "No publication bias adjustment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Expected direction of the effect"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"The expected direction of the effect. This setting is important for the "
"publication bias adjustment (one-sided selection models specify different "
"publication probabilities for estimates in the expected vs. unexpected "
"direction and PET-PEESE is bounded to adjust in the expected direction). The "
"default is 'Positive'."
msgstr ""
"Arahan terharapkan dari efek. Pengaturan ini penting untuk penyesuaian bias "
"publikasi (model pemilihan satu sisi menentukan probabilitas publikasi "
"berbeda untuk estimasi dalam arahan terharapkan vs. tidak terharapkan dan "
"PET-PEESE dibatasi untuk menyesuaikan dalam arahan terharapkan). Bawaannya "
"adalah 'Positif'."

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Detect"
msgstr "Deteksi"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Determine the expected direction of the effect automatically based on the "
"median effect size in the data."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan arah terharapkan dari efek secara otomatis berdasarkan ukuran efek "
"median dalam data."

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Positive"
msgstr "Positif"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Positive effect"
msgstr "Efek positif"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Negative"
msgstr "Negatif"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Negative effect"
msgstr "Efek negatif"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Show model specification"
msgstr "Tampilkan spesifikasi model"

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid ""
"Show the model specification. This is useful for understanding and reporting "
"the specified model."
msgstr ""
"Tampilkan spesifikasi model. Ini berguna untuk memahami dan melaporkan model "
"yang ditentukan."

msgctxt "RobustBayesianMetaAnalysis|"
msgid "Prior Distributions (Custom)"
msgstr "Distribusi Priori (Kustom)"
